stema integral\".</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Próximos pasos</h2>\n<p>Si está evaluando Paraguay seriamente, la mejor manera de avanzar es una consulta gratuita de 30 minutos. La hacemos en neerlandés, inglés, alemán o español — sin compromiso.</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"/s/es/nexa-paraguay/contacto\">Agendar consulta gratuita</a></strong></p>4:[[\"$\",\"style\",null,{\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$f\"}}],[\"$\",\"link\",null,{\"rel\":\"stylesheet\",\"href\":\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"min-h-screen\",\"style\":{\"fontFamily\":\"var(--font-body)\",\"backgroundColor\":\"var(--background)\",\"color\":\"var(--text)\"},\"children\":[\"$\",\"article\",null,{\"className\":\"bg-[var(--background)] py-16 sm:py-24\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-7xl\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"/s/es/nexa-paraguay/blog\",\"className\":\"mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-[var(--secondary)] hover:underline\",\"children\":[\"← \",\"← Blog\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--secondary)]\",\"children\":\"Tax\"}],[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"className\":\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-tight font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--text)]\",\"style\":{\"textTransform\":\"var(--heading-transform)\"},\"children\":\"Entorno fiscal de Paraguay: lo esencial explicado simple\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)]\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"time\",null,{\"dateTime\":\"2026-04-17\",\"children\":\"2026-04-17\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":[\"· \",\"Nexa Paraguay\"]}]]}],\"$undefined\",[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"prose prose-lg mt-10 max-w-none\",\"style\":{\"fontFamily\":\"var(--font-body)\",\"color\":\"var(--text)\"},\"dangerouslySetI